====格兰纳达的判决生效====
格拉纳达对瑟希案和斯特劳瑟案的裁决于2月9日起生效。正如阿拉巴马州政府那天早上照常开门一样，美国最高法院拒绝了州政府要求延缓执行的请求（[[安东宁·斯卡利亚|安东宁·斯卡利亚]]大法官与[[克拉伦斯·托马斯|克拉伦斯·托马斯]]大法官反对该判决）。<ref>{{cite news |first=Chris |last=Geidner |date=February 9, 2015 |accessdate=February 9, 2015 |work=BuzzFeed News |url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/us-supreme-court-denies-stay-in-alabama-same-sex-marriage-ca |title=U.S. Supreme Court Denies Stay In Alabama Same-Sex Marriage Case |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408064923/http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/us-supreme-court-denies-stay-in-alabama-same-sex-marriage-ca |dead-url=no }}</ref>当日，有九个县（[[奇尔顿县|奇尔顿县]]、[[科菲县_(亚拉巴马州)|科菲县]]、[[克伦肖县|克伦肖县]]、[[埃托瓦县|埃托瓦县]]、[[费耶特县_(阿拉巴马州)|费耶特县]]、[[杰佛逊县_(阿拉巴马州)|杰佛逊县]]、[[朗兹县_(亚拉巴马州)|朗兹县]]、[[麦迪逊县_(阿拉巴马州)|麦迪逊县]]和[[蒙哥马利县_(亚拉巴马州)|蒙哥马利县]]）即时开始为同性伴侣发放结婚证书。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Somashekhar|first1=Sandhya|title=Judicial defiance in Alabama: Same-sex marriages begin, but most counties refuse|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/alabama-judge-stakes-out-defiant-stance-against-same-sex-marriages/2015/02/09/a1be2de4-b06f-11e4-854b-a38d13486ba1_story.html|accessdate=February 16, 2015|work=Washington Post|date=February 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112144833/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/alabama-judge-stakes-out-defiant-stance-against-same-sex-marriages/2015/02/09/a1be2de4-b06f-11e4-854b-a38d13486ba1_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>当日第一对获得结婚证书的同性伴侣是来自蒙哥马利的托莉·希森 (Tori Sisson)和姗泰·沃尔夫 (Shanté Wolfe)。<ref>{{cite news|work=BuzzFeed News|accessdate=February 10, 2015|date=February 9, 2015|first=Sarah|last=Karlan|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/skarlan/the-love-story-behind-alabamas-first-legally-married-same-se|title=The Love Story Behind Alabama’s First Legally Married Same-Sex Couple|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919083725/https://www.buzzfeed.com/skarlan/the-love-story-behind-alabamas-first-legally-married-same-se|dead-url=no}}</ref>

9日早晨，州司法部长斯特兰奇发表了一个声明作为对最高法院判决的回应，他在声明中表示拒绝承担向同性伴侣发放结婚证书的责任，同时建议遗嘱认证法官咨询他们的法律顾问后再做出回应。<ref>{{cite web|title=Statement in Response|url=http://www.ago.state.al.us/News-594|publisher=Office of the Attorney General|accessdate=February 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114233821/http://www.ago.state.al.us/News-594|dead-url=no}}</ref>当天下午，本特利州长宣称他同意摩尔的声明和托马斯大法官的反对意见，但他表示将不会因向同性伴侣发放结婚证书而对遗嘱认证法官采取行动。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://governor.alabama.gov/newsroom/2015/02/governor-bentley-issues-statement-issuance-sex-marriage-licenses/ |title=Governor Bentley Issues Statement on Issuance of Same Sex Marriage Licenses |publisher=Office of the Governor |accessdate=February 9, 2015 |archive-date=2016-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114185052/http://governor.alabama.gov/newsroom/2015/02/governor-bentley-issues-statement-issuance-sex-marriage-licenses/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>同时，瑟希案的原告要求地区法院以藐视法庭判决为由拘捕莫比尔县的一名遗嘱法官唐·戴维斯 (Don Davis)，因为他拒绝在当天对外开放他主管的婚姻证书部门。<ref>{{cite web|website=Scribd.com|accessdate=February 9, 2015|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|title=Motion for Contempt|url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255202631|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234114/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255202631|dead-url=no}}</ref>但法庭在当天的晚些时候以戴维斯并非瑟希案诉讼当事人为由驳回了该动议。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order denying plaintiffs' motion|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/255223642/1-14-cv-00208-72|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621031234/https://www.scribd.com/doc/255223642/1-14-cv-00208-72|dead-url=no}}</ref>

