====斯特劳瑟案的进一步诉讼====
在阿拉巴马州同性婚姻合法化的第一天，斯特劳瑟案的原告方——在莫比尔县被拒绝颁发结婚证书后仅将总检察长列为被告起诉——修改了他们的诉讼书，将在法院命令生效后仍拒绝颁发同性婚姻结婚证书的遗嘱法官唐·戴维斯列为被告，并增加了三对在莫比尔县申请结婚证书的同性伴侣作为原告。原告方同时申请法庭颁布一项临时禁制令或强制令，以阻止被告执行阿拉巴马州的同性婚姻禁令，并首次向被告索要律师费赔偿。<ref>{{cite web|website=Scribd.com|accessdate=February 10, 2015|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|title=Plaintiffs' Emergency Motion|url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255246319|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222748/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255246319|dead-url=no}}</ref>法院翌日即同意了增添新当事人的请求，并安排在2月12日举行强制令的听证会。<ref>{{cite web |website=Scribd.com |publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama |accessdate=February 10, 2015 |url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255322049 |title=Order |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233307/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255322049 |dead-url=no }}</ref>听证会举办过后，格拉纳达法官对戴维斯发出了强制令，命令这位遗嘱认证法官为同性伴侣发放结婚证书，<ref>{{cite web |website=Scribd.com |accessdate=February 12, 2015 |publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama |url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/255598034/1-14-cv-00424-55-Order |title=Order |archive-date=2015-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105185114/https://www.scribd.com/doc/255598034/1-14-cv-00424-55-Order |dead-url=no }}</ref>当日下午，[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔县]]开始执行该命令。<ref name=TonerMobile>{{cite news|last1=Toner|first1=Casey|title=Gay marriage begins in Mobile (finally)|url=http://www.al.com/news/mobile/index.ssf/2015/02/gay_marriage_alabama_roy_moore_1.html|accessdate=February 12, 2015|publisher=AL.com|date=February 12, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105538/http://www.al.com/news/mobile/index.ssf/2015/02/gay_marriage_alabama_roy_moore_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月16日，[[杰佛逊县_(阿拉巴马州)|杰佛逊县]]遗嘱认证法官艾伦·金 (Alan King)——阿拉巴马州政策研究所在州法院起诉的四名遗嘱法官之一——要求地区法院允许他作为斯特劳瑟案的被告介入此案。金告诉法院，在另一起诉讼中，阿拉巴马州政策研究所和阿拉巴马州公民行动计划“共同合作并代表阿拉巴马州政府尝试不正当地寻求延长法院先前判决的延缓执行期限”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jefferson County Probate Judge Alan King's motion to intervene|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/255888429/1-14-cv-00424-58|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 16, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224837/https://www.scribd.com/doc/255888429/1-14-cv-00424-58|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月17日，斯特劳瑟案的原告方要求法院强制执行要求总检察长斯特兰奇阻止私人当事人在阿拉巴马州最高法院发起诉讼的命令，他们认为斯特兰奇有权撤销该诉讼，并指出法庭的命令对总检察长和尝试抵抗命令的私人当事人都生效。<ref>{{cite web|title=Plaintiffs' Emergency Motion for Enforcement of Injunction|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/256044277/1-14-cv-00424-60|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 17, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000041/https://www.scribd.com/doc/256044277/1-14-cv-00424-60|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾伦·金法官也提出了一项类似的动议。<ref>{{cite web|title=Proposed Intervenor King's Motion for Preliminary Injunction|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/256044273/1-14-cv-00424-59|website=Scribd,com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 17, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072205/https://www.scribd.com/doc/256044273/1-14-cv-00424-59|dead-url=no}}</ref>作为回应，斯特兰奇声称他无权指挥这样的私人当事人，以及原告在提起诉讼时的要求已得到满足，且法庭的该项命令并未要求没被列为斯特劳瑟案被告的遗嘱法官采取任何行动。<ref>{{cite web|title=Attorney General's Opposition to Plaintiffs Motion for Enforcement|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/256052840/1-14-cv-00424-62|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 17, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025049/https://www.scribd.com/doc/256052840/1-14-cv-00424-62|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月20日，格拉纳达法官回绝了金的介入请求，理由是他“似乎对这件案子的主题并没有兴趣”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order Denying Jefferson County Probate Judge Alan King's motion to intervene|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/256412388/1-14-cv-00424-66|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 20, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024719/https://www.scribd.com/doc/256412388/1-14-cv-00424-66|dead-url=no}}</ref>格拉纳达同时拒绝了原告方要求命令斯特兰奇驳回私人当事人的诉讼的请求。

====斯特劳瑟案的更多诉讼====
3月6日，戴维斯要求联邦法院延迟执行斯特劳瑟案的判决，他在辩词中称他向原告开出结婚证书已经满足了联邦法院的具体要求，以及若阿拉巴马州最高法院决定增添原告中同性伴侣的个数并要求他为他们发放结婚证书的话他将只能遵守该要求。他指出，他对阿拉巴马州剥夺同性伴侣婚姻权利的宪法性基本法律问题不持公开立场，并描述了他因为联邦法院和州法院发出的的命令不相同甚至相左而被迫陷入了一个“前所未有的，历史性的，但困难的境地”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Don Davis Emergency Motion for Stay|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/257845241/1-14-cv-00424-71|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 7, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042709/https://www.scribd.com/doc/257845241/1-14-cv-00424-71|dead-url=no}}</ref>格拉纳达法官随后立即要求原告方面在3月13日的期限之前对戴维斯的请求作出回应。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order: Plaintiffs to file response to motion for stay by Friday, March 13, 2015|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/257883124/1-14-cv-00424-72|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 7, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222158/https://www.scribd.com/doc/257883124/1-14-cv-00424-72|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月6日晚些时候，正如戴维斯所预料的一样，斯特劳瑟案的原告方要求格拉纳达法官在斯特劳瑟案中添加原告和被告以及书面证明这是一起[[集体诉讼|集体诉讼]]。他们将三对同性伴侣加入原告名单中，并声称他/她们“代表了其他有类似遭遇的人”，这三对伴侣都曾被拒绝发放结婚证书。原告同时将[[鲍德温县_(亚拉巴马州)|鲍德温县]]的遗嘱法官蒂姆·罗素 (Tim Russell)列入被告名单中“作为（与戴维斯）相近立场的阿拉巴马州遗嘱法官的代表”。原告方的律师们表示[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]、{{link-en|美国政教分离联合会|Americans United for Separation of Church and State}}和[[美国公民自由联盟|美国公民自由联盟]]阿拉巴马州支部都加入了支持国家女同性恋权利中心的阵营。<ref>{{cite web|title=Second Motion to Amend Complaint|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/257913372/1-14-cv-00424-76|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 7, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060702/https://www.scribd.com/doc/257913372/1-14-cv-00424-76|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Geidner|first1=Chris|title=LGBT Legal Groups Seeks Statewide Ruling In Alabama’s Federal Court Marriage Case|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/lgbt-legal-groups-seeks-statewide-ruling-in-alabamas-federal|accessdate=7 March 2015|work=BuzzFeed News|date=March 6, 2015|archive-date=2016-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429113815/https://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/lgbt-legal-groups-seeks-statewide-ruling-in-alabamas-federal|dead-url=no}}</ref>法庭要求戴维斯法官在3月17日前对此作出回应。

3月13日，[[麦迪逊县_(阿拉巴马州)|麦迪逊县]]巡回法官卡伦·霍尔 (Karen Hall)批准了一桩由一对[[2012年11月|2012年11月]]在爱荷华州登记结婚的女同性恋伴侣提出的离婚请求。值得一提的是，霍尔法官在一年前曾拒绝过这对伴侣的同样请求。<ref>{{cite news| agency= Associated Press| work= New York Times| date= March 13, 2015| accessdate= March 13, 2015| url= http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/03/13/us/ap-us-gay-marriage-alabama.html| title= With Gay Marriage on Hold, Alabama Judge OKs Lesbian Divorce| archive-date= 2015-04-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150419025954/http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/03/13/us/ap-us-gay-marriage-alabama.html| dead-url= no}}</ref>

3月16日，格拉纳达法官驳回了戴维斯要求延缓执行斯特劳瑟案判决的请求<ref>{{cite web|title=Order Denying Davis's Motion to Stay February 12 preliminary injunction order|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/258953112/1-14-cv-00424-88|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 16, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075042/https://www.scribd.com/doc/258953112/1-14-cv-00424-88|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于次日将要求他回应原告诉求的期限延长至3月23日。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order setting deadline for Attorney General to respond|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/259073763/1-14-cv-00424-89|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 17, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084415/https://www.scribd.com/doc/259073763/1-14-cv-00424-89|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日，戴维斯对诉求作出回应。3月18日，格拉纳达法官接受原告增加当事人的要求。对于州检察长提出的关于本案判决“矫枉过正”的抗议，格拉纳达回应道：“[原告获得的]证书如果在阿拉巴马州未被认定为有效，则没有价值。”<ref>{{cite web |website=Scribd.com |date=March 28, 2015 |accessdate=March 18, 2015 |url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/259206591 |title=Order |publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225045/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/259206591 |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月23日，她否决了检察总长的废除动议。

5月21日，格拉纳达法官将案件定为集体诉讼，并命令该州所有的遗嘱认证法官以及与他们职权相同的人在婚姻平等的基础上，无论州宪法、法令或州最高法院的判决如何，都要为同性伴侣发放结婚证书。但她表示将暂缓执行[[禁制令|禁制令]]，以等待最高法院的进一步行动。<ref>{{cite news| first= Chris| last= Geidner| accessdate= May 21, 2015| date= May 21, 2015| work= BuzzFeed News| title= Federal Judge Expands Alabama Marriage Ruling Statewide, But Puts Order On Hold| url= http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/federal-judge-expands-alabama-marriage-ruling-statewide-but#.usQmxwrMg1| archive-date= 2016-03-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065048/http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/federal-judge-expands-alabama-marriage-ruling-statewide-but#.usQmxwrMg1| dead-url= no}}</ref>

====斯特劳瑟案的最终禁制令====
2016年6月7日，卡丽·格拉纳达法官发出永久禁制令，禁止任何州官员执行不承认同性伴侣的婚姻权利的法律。<ref name="EndStrawser">{{cite web |url=http://wkrg.com/2016/06/09/another-victory-for-same-sex-couple-in-federal-lawsuit/ |author=Quynh, Jacqueline |title=Another Victory for Same Sex Couple in Federal Lawsuit |publisher=WKRG |date=June 9, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-06 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818034541/http://wkrg.com/2016/06/09/another-victory-for-same-sex-couple-in-federal-lawsuit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-marriage-idUSKCN0YU2SY |author=Brooks, Karen |title=Judge issues final order upholding Alabama same-sex marriage |publisher=Reuters |date=June 9, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-06 |archive-date=2016-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805210121/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-marriage-idUSKCN0YU2SY |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===赫奇佩思诉戴维斯 (''Hedgepeth v. Davis'')===
2月9日晚些时候，瑟西案的律师代表八对于2月9日当天在莫比尔县被拒发结婚许可的伴侣提起了一个新的诉讼——赫奇佩思诉戴维斯案，他们将戴维斯和他的两名员工、本特利州长、斯特兰吉总检察长和首席大法官摩尔列为被告。他们向法庭寻求颁发紧急禁制令和制裁。<ref>{{cite web|title=Complaint and request for immediate injunctive relief|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/255235097/1-15-cv-00067-1-Complaint|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630235805/https://www.scribd.com/doc/255235097/1-15-cv-00067-1-Complaint|dead-url=no}}</ref>戴维斯要求阿拉巴马州最高法院根据美国最高法院的判决和瑟西案中已被驳回的<ref>{{cite news|last1=Tillman|first1=Zoe|title=Clash Over Alabama Gay Marriage Licenses Heads to Court|url=http://www.nationallawjournal.com/home/id=1202717514094/Clash-Over-Alabama-Gay-Marriage-Licenses-Heads-to-Court|accessdate=February 10, 2015|work=National Law Journal|date=February 10, 2015|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713115641/https://www.law.com/nationallawjournal/?slreturn=20190613075640|dead-url=no}}</ref>蔑视法庭罪动议做出进一步指示，法院在2月11日指这是一项{{link-en|意见咨询|Advisory opinion}}请求，而最高法院仅有权向州长和立法机关提供此类咨询，因此拒绝了戴维斯的要求。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://acis.alabama.gov/displaydocs.cfm?no=638333&event=4A30ZSZFE:|title=Order Ex Parte Don Davis|accessdate=February 11, 2015|publisher=Alabama Judicial System|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107014909/https://acis.alabama.gov/displaydocs.cfm?no=638333&event=4A30ZSZFE:|dead-url=no}}</ref>地区法院以程序原因为由拒绝为赫奇佩思案的原告提供立即救济，但表示将邀请他们的律师参加2月12日举行的斯特劳瑟案听证会。<ref>{{cite web|website=Scribd.com|accessdate=February 10, 2015|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255344981|title=Order|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630221629/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/255344981|dead-url=no}}</ref>在莫比尔县同意为同性伴侣发放结婚证书之后，原告同意将县官员移除出被告名单，此时被告只剩下斯特兰吉和摩尔二人。3月24日，在成功得到结婚证书后，原告向法院提出撤诉。

===阿拉巴马州政策研究所的诉讼===
2015年2月11日，两个保守派组织，{{link-en|阿拉巴马州政策研究所|Alabama Policy Institute}}和阿拉巴马州公民行动计划，向该州最高法院提起诉讼，要求禁止该州的遗嘱法官为同性伴侣颁发结婚证。<ref>{{cite news |accessdate=February 13, 2015 |date=February 11, 2015 |publisher=Washington Post |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/some-alabama-counties-refuse-gay-marriages-prompting-suit/2015/02/10/599c66ee-b18b-11e4-bf39-5560f3918d4b_story.html |title=Groups ask Alabama Supreme Court to stop gay weddings |archive-date=2015-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214055259/http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/some-alabama-counties-refuse-gay-marriages-prompting-suit/2015/02/10/599c66ee-b18b-11e4-bf39-5560f3918d4b_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{efn|该案被称为“阿拉巴马州代表阿拉巴马州政策研究所和阿拉巴马州公民行动计划单方面诉金”或“阿拉巴马州诉金”}} 这起诉讼虽然只列出了四名遗嘱认证法官的名字，但针对的是该州内的所有相同职位人员。2月13日，{{link-en|平等阿拉巴马|Equality Alabama}}提交了一份法院之友简报，要求最高法院驳回政策研究所的诉讼。简报指出，原告并没有表明他们遭受到了具体的伤害，并且不正当地试图担任州政府官员的角色。<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=February 13, 2015|url=http://freemarry.3cdn.net/e7580e671d9303b754_p9m6iv923.PDF|title=Brief of Amicus Curiae Equality Alabama|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101953/http://freemarry.3cdn.net/e7580e671d9303b754_p9m6iv923.PDF|dead-url=no}}</ref>法院要求四名被告于2月18日前提交简报，允许原告在2月23日上午10时前作出回复。其中一名被告戴维斯法官认为这起诉讼假设格拉纳达法官的判决对遗嘱法官没有约束力，且由于他已经被列为斯特劳瑟案的被告，因此此案并不适用于他。<ref>{{cite web | accessdate=February 18, 2015 | url=https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/256198278 | website=Scribd.com | title=Response of Judge Don Davis | publisher=Alabama Supreme Court | archive-date=2016-04-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403181715/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/256198278 | dead-url=no }}</ref>艾伦·金和汤米·拉格兰 (Tommy Ragland)法官提出了与平等阿拉巴马类似的观点。<ref>{{cite web | accessdate= February 18, 2015 | title= Respondents King and Ragland's Joint Answer | url= https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/256198385 | publisher= Alabama Supreme Court | archive-date= 2016-04-03 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160403184428/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/256198385 | dead-url= no }}</ref>3月3日，法庭以7-1的比数裁定原告拥有起诉资格，且阿拉巴马州的同性婚姻禁令不违反美国宪法，并命令所有遗嘱法官遵守阿拉巴马州法律，不为同性伴侣发放结婚证书。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/04/us/alabama-court-orders-halt-to-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|title = Alabama Court Orders a Halt to Same-Sex Marriage Licenses|last = Robertson|first = Campbell|date = March 3, 2015|work = New York Times|access-date = March 4, 2015|archive-date = 2017-01-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170108012140/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/04/us/alabama-court-orders-halt-to-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>法庭要求受格拉纳达判决限制的戴维斯法官于3月5日之前解释他是否在除斯特劳瑟案原告之外还被强制要求发放结婚证书。5日，戴维斯向法庭申请将回复期限延长10日。<ref>{{cite web|title=ODavis Brief in support of motion to extend deadline|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/257824842/1140460-Davis-Brief-in-Support|website=Scribd.com|publisher=Alabama Supreme Court|accessdate=March 7, 2015|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403181717/https://www.scribd.com/doc/257824842/1140460-Davis-Brief-in-Support|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月11日，法庭拒绝了戴维斯的延期请求并命令他不能再向任何同性伴侣颁发新的结婚证书。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order enjoining Davis|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/258388759/1140460-ORDER-Enjoining-Davis|website=Scribd.com|publisher=Alabama Supreme Court|accessdate=March 11, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075449/https://www.scribd.com/doc/258388759/1140460-ORDER-Enjoining-Davis|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据阿拉巴马州最高法院3月3日的命令，戴维斯法官关闭了莫比尔县的婚姻登记处。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Geidner|first1=Chris|title=Alabama Probate Judge Faces Conflicting Commands In Same-Sex Marriage Cases|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/alabama-probate-judge-faces-conflicting-commands-in-same-sex|accessdate=March 17, 2015|work=BuzzFeed News|date=March 17, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093012/http://www.buzzfeed.com/chrisgeidner/alabama-probate-judge-faces-conflicting-commands-in-same-sex|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月18日，[[蒙哥马利县_(亚拉巴马州)|蒙哥马利县]]遗嘱法官{{link-en|斯蒂文·里德|Steven Reed (judge)}}要求法院修改其命令，以保证将来若美国最高法院裁定禁止同性婚姻违宪时该命令不会与其抵触。<ref>{{cite web| website= Scribd.com| date= March 18, 2015| accessdate= March 18, 2015| publisher= Alabama Supreme Court| url= https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/259185239| title= Application for Rehearing| archive-date= 2016-03-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035820/https://www.scribd.com/mobile/doc/259185239| dead-url= no}}</ref>法庭在3月23日否决了他的要求，但没有作出解释。<ref>{{cite web|title=Order denying Judge Reed's application for rehearing|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/259672214/1140460-Order|website=Scribd.com|publisher=Alabama Supreme Court|accessdate=March 23, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070523/https://www.scribd.com/doc/259672214/1140460-Order|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===瑟希诉戴维斯 (''Searcy v. Davis'')===
2015年2月24日，卡丽·瑟希要求地区法院对遗嘱法官唐·戴维斯发出禁制令，原因是戴维斯在接受瑟希诉斯特兰吉案的判决而颁布初步通过令时在其中加入了一段话，表示“本命令具有合法性，但本法院在美国最高法院就婚姻法案件做出最后判决之前不会颁布最终通过令”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Complaint and Request for Preliminary and Permanent Injunctive Relief|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/256833075/1-15-cv-00104-1|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S> District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=February 25, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630233800/https://www.scribd.com/doc/256833075/1-15-cv-00104-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月24日，瑟希知会法庭，表示戴维斯已经删除了有关段落并要求法院驳回她的诉讼。<ref>{{cite web|title=Motion to Dismiss|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/259864639/1-15-cv-00104-34|website=Scribd.com|publisher=U.S. District Court for Southern Alabama|accessdate=March 25, 2015|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701011506/https://www.scribd.com/doc/259864639/1-15-cv-00104-34|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===美国最高法院判决===
6月26日，美国最高法院在[[奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案|奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案]]中裁定剥夺同性伴侣的婚姻权利是违宪的。阿拉巴马州检察长路德·斯特兰奇在一篇新闻稿中写道：“尽管我不同意多数大法官在这个决定中的意见，但我承认美国最高法院的裁决现在成为了这里的法律。”<ref name=campoflores>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/law/2015/06/27/alabama-probate-judges-begin-issuing-licenses-for-same-sex-marriages/|title=Alabama Probate Judges Begin Issuing Licenses for Same-Sex Marriages|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=June 27, 2015|author=Arian Campo-Flores|accessdate=June 29, 2015|archive-date=2016-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126011441/http://blogs.wsj.com/law/2015/06/27/alabama-probate-judges-begin-issuing-licenses-for-same-sex-marriages/|dead-url=no}}</ref>当天开始，一些遗嘱法官——包括伯明翰县和莫比尔县——开始发放结婚许可证，然而仍有部分法官拒绝为同性伴侣发放结婚证书或者甚至直接不为任何伴侣发放。<ref name=campoflores/>2015年6月27日，美国公民自由联盟阿拉巴马支部要求该州的遗嘱法官协会指示其成员遵守裁决。<ref name=campoflores/>截至2015年6月29日，该州67个县中的至少32个县已经开始为同性伴侣颁发结婚许可证，但仍有至少22个县拒绝这么做。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2015/06/at_least_22_alabama_counties_r.html#incart_story_package |title=At least 22 Alabama counties will not issue same-sex marriage licenses |accessdate=2016-12-11 |archive-date=2016-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920185705/http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2015/06/at_least_22_alabama_counties_r.html#incart_story_package |dead-url=no }}</ref>同样在当日，县委员会协会——一个为法官提供责任保险的组织——建议该州法官遵守美国最高法院的判决。<ref>{{cite news |publisher=WIAT |url=http://wiat.com/2015/06/29/alabama-supreme-court-orderalabama-supreme-court-order-creates-confusion-over-same-sex-marriage-licenses-creates-confusion-over-same-sex-licenses/ |title=Alabama Supreme Court order creates confusion over same-sex marriage licenses |first=Haley |last=Townsend |accessdate=2016-12-11 |archive-date=2016-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420071432/http://wiat.com/2015/06/29/alabama-supreme-court-orderalabama-supreme-court-order-creates-confusion-over-same-sex-marriage-licenses-creates-confusion-over-same-sex-licenses/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在奥贝格费尔案的判决出炉后，阿拉巴马州最高法院首席法官摩尔指出，该判决需要重新审议25日，在结束之前不具有约束力。阿拉巴马州最高法院在这25日之间呼吁社会提供对阿拉巴马州政策研究所一案判决（不发放结婚证书）的[[法院之友|法院之友]]简报。<ref name=walksback>{{cite news|accessdate=June 29, 2015|date=June 29, 2015|work=The Hill|title=Alabama chief justice walks back remarks on same-sex marriage|url=http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/246467-alabama-chief-justice-moves-to-delay-same-sex-marriage|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914085321/http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/246467-alabama-chief-justice-moves-to-delay-same-sex-marriage|dead-url=no}}</ref>摩尔后来发表了一份澄清声明，写道：“[阿拉巴马州最高法院的]命令绝不会为本州的遗嘱法官提供是否应该遵守美国最高法院的奥贝格费尔案判决的指示。”<ref name=walksback/> 7月1日，斯特劳瑟案原告方要求格拉纳达法官明确先前被搁置的禁制令的状态，<ref>{{cite web|title=Plaintiffs' Motion for Clarification as to Preliminary Injunction Order|url=http://files.eqcf.org/cases/114-cv-00424-144/|website=Equality Case Files|accessdate=July 1, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304134829/http://files.eqcf.org/cases/114-cv-00424-144/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日格拉纳达即作出澄清，她发出命令指出先前初步的禁制令现在正式生效并适用于该州所有的遗嘱法官。<ref>{{cite web |title=Order granting motion for clarification |url=http://files.eqcf.org/cases/114-cv-00424-145/ |website=Equality Case Files |accessdate=July 1, 2015 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806122744/http://files.eqcf.org/cases/114-cv-00424-145/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

