州)|谢尔比县]]（除非直接命令否则不会发放）、[[华盛顿郡_(亚拉巴马州)|华盛顿郡]]（等待美国最高法院判决）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2015/02/13/a-majority-of-alabama-counties-are-now-issuing-same-sex-marriage-licenses/ |title=A majority of Alabama counties are now issuing same-sex marriage licenses |accessdate=2016-12-16 |archive-date=2016-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161215042158/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2015/02/13/a-majority-of-alabama-counties-are-now-issuing-same-sex-marriage-licenses/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

