.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[马歇尔县_(亚拉巴马州)|马歇尔县]]（曾经计划发放但已取消）、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wsfa.com/story/28130404/marshall-co-halts-issuing-all-marriage-licenses |title=Marshall Co. halts issuing all marriage licenses |access-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804160649/http://www.wsfa.com/story/28130404/marshall-co-halts-issuing-all-marriage-licenses |archive-date=2016-08-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[派克县_(亚拉巴马州)|派克县]]、[[兰道夫县_(亚拉巴马州)|兰道夫县]]、[[沃克县_(亚拉巴马州)|沃克县]]

