===州最高法院判决之后 ===
[[File:Same-sex_marriage_in_Alabama_by_county_(peak_refusal_2015).svg|thumb]]
2015年3月15日，阿拉巴马州最高法院下令州内所有遗嘱法官停止向同性伴侣发放结婚证。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/04/us/alabama-court-orders-halt-to-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|title = Alabama Court Orders a Halt to Same-Sex Marriage Licenses|last = Robertson|first = Campbell|date = March 3, 2015|work = New York Times|accessdate = March 4, 2015|archive-date = 2017-01-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170108012140/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/04/us/alabama-court-orders-halt-to-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>到翌日下午，所有或几乎所有的县{{efn|一个消息来源指出3月4日梅肯县仍在发放这类结婚证书：[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/03/04/alabama-marriage_n_6801412.html 阿拉巴马州停止向同性伴侣发放结婚证书] 这种情况有可能发生在上午，因为根据其它消息来源报道，到下午时梅肯县已经停止该服务。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hrc.org/press-releases/entry/hrc-unable-to-confirm-any-al-counties-issuing-licenses-to-same-sex-couples |title=HRC Unable to Confirm Any AL Counties Issuing Licenses to Same-Sex Couples |accessdate=2016-12-16 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002061755/http://www.hrc.org/press-releases/entry/hrc-unable-to-confirm-any-al-counties-issuing-licenses-to-same-sex-couples |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}都停止了许可证的发放。奥陶加县、梅肯县、莫比尔县<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/marriage-equality-grinds-halt-alabama |title=Marriage equality grinds to a halt in Alabama |accessdate=2016-12-16 |archive-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809025633/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/marriage-equality-grinds-halt-alabama |dead-url=no }}</ref>和塔拉迪加县则停止向所有伴侣发放证书。先前已对同性伴侣停止该服务的查克托县和杰尼瓦县也停止了向异性伴侣提供该服务，而先前已不再为任何伴侣服务的比伯县、克拉克县、休斯敦县、马歇尔县、派克县、兰道夫县和沃克县则延续了这一政策。<ref name=ALMarriage/>

==美国最高法院判决之后==
===立法工作===
2015年9月16日，[[亚拉巴马州众议院|阿拉巴马州众议院]]在一次表决中以53-36的比数支持了一项旨在废除由州颁发的结婚证的法案，旨在使阿拉巴马州得以从婚姻争议中脱身。支持者表示这项法案将会保护反对向同性伴侣发放结婚证书的遗嘱认证法官。然而该法案由于未获得至少2/3多数（70票）的支持而未获通过，尽管[[亚拉巴马州参议院|阿拉巴马州参议院]]先前已为该法案开了绿灯。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wtok.com/home/headlines/Alabama-Marriage-License-Vote-328051831.html |title=Alabama Marriage License Vote |publisher=WTOK.com |date=September 17, 2015 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826120218/http://www.wtok.com/home/headlines/Alabama-Marriage-License-Vote-328051831.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年3月15日，阿拉巴马州参议院在不需要三分之二多数（24票）支持的情况下以23-3的比数通过了一个类似上文提及的法案（即旨在废除州颁发的结婚证）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2016/03/alabama_senate_approves_replac.html |title=Alabama Senate approves replacing marriage licenses with contracts |publisher=AL.com |date=March 15, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027090846/http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2016/03/alabama_senate_approves_replac.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefrisky.com/2016-03-16/alabama-senate-decides-to-abolish-marriage-licenses-rather-than-give-them-to-gay-couples/ |title=Alabama Senate Decides To Abolish Marriage Licenses Rather Than Give Them To Gay Couples |access-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914215139/http://www.thefrisky.com/2016-03-16/alabama-senate-decides-to-abolish-marriage-licenses-rather-than-give-them-to-gay-couples/ |archive-date=2016-09-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但这个法案在州众议院未经投票即夭折。

===各县的情况===
截至2015年10月2日，至少有八个县（奥陶加县、乔克托县、克拉克县、克利本县、卡温顿县、杰尼瓦县、派克县和华盛顿县）在没有说明是否或何时将恢复的情况下仍处于停止发放任何结婚证书的状态。<ref name="ballotpedia">{{Cite web |url=http://ballotpedia.org/Local_government_responses_to_Obergefell_v._Hodges |title=Local government responses to Obergefell v. Hodges |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115180139/https://ballotpedia.org/Local_government_responses_to_Obergefell_v._Hodges |dead-url=no }}</ref>钱伯斯县和比伯县分别于8月21日和9月4日确认它们将不会颁发任何结婚证书。<ref name="ballotpedia"/> 但到2016年6月26日，钱伯斯县已开始向所有伴侣发放结婚证。<ref name="Blade"/>

埃尔莫尔县、麦迪逊县、马伦戈县、莫比尔县和沃克县在2016年1月6日的罗伊·摩尔法官得判决之后便停止了发放结婚证的服务（见下文）。然而，麦迪逊县、莫比尔县和沃克县在几日后又重新为所有伴侣开放了此服务。<ref name="Issue1"/><ref name="Issue2"/>

在格拉纳达法官的斯特劳瑟诉斯特兰吉案最终禁制令（见上文）发出后，克拉克县和华盛顿县的遗嘱法庭都重申他们不会为同性伴侣亦或异性伴侣发放结婚证书。<ref name="EndStrawser"/>

====一年后====
[[File:Same-sex_marriage_in_Alabama_by_county.svg|thumb]]
在奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案一周年纪念日的几天前，阿拉巴马州的美国公民自由联盟发布调查，指出州内仍有12个县拒绝为同性伴侣发放结婚证书，其中11个县（奥陶加县、比伯县、查克托县、克拉克县、克利本县、卡温顿县、埃尔莫尔县、杰尼瓦县、马伦戈县、派克县和华盛顿县）不为任何伴侣发放，无论同性或异性，剩下的一个[[库萨县|库萨县]]以“技术困难”为由（却又承认没有改善计划）唯独拒绝承认同性伴侣的结婚许可证的合法性。<ref name="Blade">{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonblade.com/2016/06/22/one-year-after-supreme-court-ruling-pockets-of-marriage-inequality-remain/ |author=Johnson, Chris |title=One year after marriage ruling, pockets of defiance remain |publisher=[[Washington_Blade|Washington Blade]] |date=June 22, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128221201/https://www.washingtonblade.com/2016/06/22/one-year-after-supreme-court-ruling-pockets-of-marriage-inequality-remain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

至2016年10月，比伯县、库萨县和马伦戈县已开始不分性别地为伴侣提供结婚证书服务，而其余9个县则坚持拒绝发放任何婚姻许可证。<ref name="ala2016oct">{{Cite news|url=http://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/10/at_least_8_alabama_counties_st.html|title=Eight Alabama counties still refuse to issue marriage licenses despite gay marriage ruling|newspaper=AL.com|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181024035146/https://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/10/at_least_8_alabama_counties_st.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而至少有6个允许发放结婚许可证的县拒绝主持任何婚礼仪式。<ref name="ala2016oct"/>

===罗伊·摩尔的判决===
2016年1月6日，阿拉巴马州首席大法官罗伊·摩尔再次命令州内的遗嘱法官停止为同性伴侣发放结婚证书。摩尔指出，2015年的美国最高法院判决于先前的阿拉巴马州最高法院判决相矛盾，因此州最高法院需要澄清这一情况。他还补充道，这一判决并未使该州的宪法修正案失去效力，因为它仅对被告方（[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]、[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]、[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]和[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]）生效。<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-gaymarriage-idUSKBN0UK2AR20160106?utm_source=Facebook Alabama chief justice orders halt to same-sex marriage licenses] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-gaymarriage-idUSKBN0UK2AR20160106?utm_source=Facebook |date=20160406153457 }}". ''Reuters''. January 6, 2016.</ref>然而，只有五个遗嘱法庭（埃尔莫尔县、麦迪逊县、马伦戈县、莫比尔县和沃克县）听从了摩尔的命令，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2016/01/07/alabama-same-sex-marriage/78436564/ |title=A few Ala. counties halt marriage licenses to gay couples |publisher=USA TODAY |date=January 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107020618/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2016/01/07/alabama-same-sex-marriage/78436564/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而其中三个（麦迪逊县、莫比尔县和沃克县）在几日之后便重新开始为同性伴侣发放结婚证书。<ref name="Issue1">{{cite web |url=http://www.advocate.com/marriage-equality/2016/1/20/least-11-alabama-counties-refuse-comply-marriage-equality |author=Broverman, Neal |title=At Least 11 Alabama Counties Refuse to Comply With Marriage Equality |publisher=[[The_Advocate|The Advocate]] |date=January 20, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010212231/http://www.advocate.com/marriage-equality/2016/1/20/least-11-alabama-counties-refuse-comply-marriage-equality |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Issue2">{{cite web |url=http://www.al.com/news/mobile/index.ssf/2016/01/more_legal_action_on_the_way_i.html |author=Toner, Casey |title=Mobile County to issue marriage licenses (again) |publisher=Alabama Local News |date=January 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010042023/http://www.al.com/news/mobile/index.ssf/2016/01/more_legal_action_on_the_way_i.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-alabama-same-sex-20160112-story.html| title=Gay marriage order puts spotlight again on the 'Ayatollah of Alabama'| first=Jenny| last=Jarvie| work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]| date=2016-01-13| accessdate=2016-01-13| archive-date=2016-01-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113135112/http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-alabama-same-sex-20160112-story.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>这个命令并未实际生效，州内所有的县要么为所有伴侣继续发放结婚证书要么则继续不为任何伴侣发放。[[2016年5月|2016年5月]]，摩尔因此命令收到了来自州司法调查委员会的道德指控。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-gaymarriage-idUSKCN0XY042|title=Alabama's top judge faces ethics charges over gay-marriage order|work=Reuters|date=7 May 2016|accessdate=2016-12-22|archive-date=2017-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208014247/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-alabama-gaymarriage-idUSKCN0XY042|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月30日，摩尔被判有罪，他的余下任期被暂停。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/01/us/roy-moore-alabama-chief-justice.html?_r=0 Roy Moore, Alabama Chief Justice, Suspended Over Gay Marriage Order] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/01/us/roy-moore-alabama-chief-justice.html?_r=0 |date=20170206042718 }} The New York Times</ref>

===阿拉巴马州最高法院===
2016年3月4日，阿拉巴马州最高法院作出一项判决，驳回了阿拉巴马政策研究所、阿拉巴马公民行动计划和埃尔莫尔县遗嘱法官共同提出的上诉请求，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://acis.alabama.gov/displaydocs.cfm?no=721120&event=4KW0LCPOJ |title=Alabama Supreme Court, order, March 4, 2016. |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2017-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170203025919/https://acis.alabama.gov/displaydocs.cfm?no=721120&event=4KW0LCPOJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但法院并未明确表示是否承认美国最高法院在奥贝格费尔案中的判决成为该州法律。该判决的预期效果并不明显：虽然判决貌似承认了奥贝格费尔案后该州通过的意在挑战其合法性的司法判决是无效的，但它并没有明确承认美国最高法院的判决进入该州法律，还反倒提出了该判决无效的意见。<ref name="Faulk-2016">Randall C. Marshall, quoted in Kent Faulk, [http://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/03/alabama_supreme_court_dismisse.html "Alabama Supreme Court dismisses petitions opposing gay marriage"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/03/alabama_supreme_court_dismisse.html |date=20160814171545 }}, AL.com, March 4, 2016.</ref>阿拉巴马州的美国公民自由联盟法律总监指出：“在原命令之后呈交的所有动议/请愿书都被驳回了，唯独不动原命令。但这一命令由于奥贝格费尔案和斯特劳瑟案对全州遗嘱法官的禁制令的存在，现在（根据肖法官的说法）形同一纸空文。”<ref name="Faulk-2016" />[[福音派|福音派]]基督教法律组织{{link-en|自由律师会|Liberty Counsel}}赞同道：“该判决使阿拉巴马州最高法院对遗嘱法官发出的禁止为同性伴侣发放结婚证书的命令永久化，州最高法院已拒绝执行五名美国最高法院律师的非法意见。”<ref name="Faulk-2016" />

尽管这项命令的预期效果不明确，但法院的法官们仍发布了若干协同意见书。格雷格·肖 (Greg Shaw)法官的协同意见书中的一个评论认为，阿拉巴马州最高法院必须遵守美国最高法院的判决，而不遵循该原则的大法官理应辞职。<ref name="Faulk-2016" />

==婚姻数据==
根据阿拉巴马州公共卫生部门的统计，至少有545对同性伴侣在2015年2月9日至3月3日期间已获得结婚许可证并喜结良缘。<ref>{{cite news | accessdate= April 10, 2015 | title= More than 500 same-sex couples married in Alabama | url= http://m.decaturdaily.com/news/other_news/state/more-than-same-sex-couples-married-in-alabama/article_af1f0463-dc7c-5c39-b22a-c3c833319800.html | date= April 9, 2015 | work= Decatur Daily | agency= Associated Press | archive-date= 2019-07-13 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190713115645/https://www.decaturdaily.com/news/other_news/state/more-than-same-sex-couples-married-in-alabama/article_af1f0463-dc7c-5c39-b22a-c3c833319800.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>

截至2015年底，共有1622起同性婚姻得到认证。同性婚姻占该年该州婚姻总数的4%。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/06/how_many_same-sex_couples_marr.html |author=Cason, Mike |title=How many same-sex couples married in Alabama the first year they could? |publisher=Alabama Local News |date=June 23, 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011150536/http://www.al.com/news/birmingham/index.ssf/2016/06/how_many_same-sex_couples_marr.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

